            <sectiondiv outputclass="Activity">
              <sectiondiv outputclass="activity.question">
                <p>
                  <b>1</b> Round a measurement of 1.059 metres:</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <p>(a) to the nearest whole number of metres;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <p>(b) to two decimal places;</p>
                  </li>
                  
                </ul>
            </sectiondiv>
              <sectiondiv outputclass="Answer">
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <p>(a) 1.059 m rounded to the nearest whole number of metres is 1
                      m.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <p>(b) 1.059 m rounded to two decimal places is 1.06 m.</p>
                  </li>
                  
                </ul>
              </sectiondiv>
            </sectiondiv>
